**Summary:** This documentation explains the progressive migration process from Amplitude SDK to Ampli, covering three phases: SDK-only, SDK+Ampli hybrid using `ampli.load({ client: { instance: amplitude }})`, and Ampli-only implementation with strongly typed event tracking methods like `ampli.songPlayed()` and `ampli.track(new SongPlayed())`.

